ost used, and cheapest to make poisons? <br><br>7) I have a SCS (not a twinky until I give it to my new guy ;] ) and a whip of strangulation (not a twinky yet either, but a VERY nice price). Do these weapons pair up well? I know the SCS doesn't proc till at least 41-42, but the stats are still nice on it. If I were to upgrade my weapons, what would be the next step? <br><br>8) I currently have a kunzar cloak on the guy I have to delete which is the only item I have that is not barbie wearable (imagine that, my old guy is a gnome and I'm twinking a barbie yet only one thing won't be wearable). What would replace this item well? <br><br>9) I am sort of set on how I'm going to spend my 30 starting points on my barbie, but not completely. I was thinking leave the 103 str how it is (it's not to shabby), put a bunch into dex to get it caught up with the other rogue stats, a few into agi (just cause), and the leftovers into sta (a few people say it's an important stat). I know many will disagree with my stat spending, so correct me PLZ. <br><br>10) How much wood coulda wood chuck chuck if a wood chuck could chuck wood? (hey, I had to make it an even 10) <br><br>Thnx fer answering! If you have any other suggestions to help me get it right this time PLZ post 'em. Donka shan and PEACE! <br><br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=2><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=2&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=2&mid=99996334046236&num=0&post=1&mid=99996334046236><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Re